CustomField.description: The API name of a field set used by the Project Task object. This set defines the project task fields (if associated tasks exist) to copy from a template to a new project. These fields are not displayed during creation of the project.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: The API name of a field set used by the Project Task object. This set defines the project task fields (if associated tasks exist) to copy from a template to a new project. These fields are not displayed during creation of the project.
CustomField.label: Project Task Hidden
